content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 938.9 - Duty to Correct

State Regulations

As with any filing required to be submitted to the

Commission, Client Filers have a duty to file accurate and complete reports. Client Filers therefore have a duty to correct any oversights or inaccuracies
within 10 days of discovery. Notes
